Qwen3.6 recurrent shrink/expand prompt-cache patch for stock llama.cpp.

Source: Reddit r/LocalLLM post 1ullrvq / Pastebin E55YG5NS.
Based on upstream PR: ggml-org/llama.cpp#24785
(`server: add recurrent state shrink/expand for prompt cache (#22746)`).

Adds recurrent memory shrink/expand APIs and shrinks recurrent state around
prompt-cache update operations, then expands back to user parallelism. This is
experimental and should be dropped when equivalent upstream support is merged.

